name: pETH
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: pETH is an Ethereum derivative supported by the JPEG'd protocol. It is minted when a user borrows against their NFT and burned when they decide to repay their loan. Unlike the 2% interest rate for borrowing PUSd, minting $pETH against an NFT has a 5% interest rate.
